Module scrabble.main

Package cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IOperations
    This interface contains mathematical operations for Scr objects (int and float) It contains additions, subtractions, multiplications and divitions
    LogicalOp
    This interface contains Logical operations for Scr objects (binary and bool) It contains logic and, or & negation
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ScrBinary
    The ScrBinary class wraps an String consisting of only '0' and '1' that represents a signed int.
    ScrBool
    The ScrBool class wraps a boolean in an object.
    ScrFloat
    The ScrFloat class wraps a double in an object.
    ScrInt
    The ScrInt class wraps an int in an object.
    ScrString
    The ScrString class wraps a String in an object.
